export async function getBlogDetails(id) {
  //return await request("/blogs/" + id);
  let requestedBlog = null;
  for (let blog of blogs) {
    if (blog.id === id) {
      requestedBlog = blog;
    }
  }
  return {
    data: requestedBlog,
    status: requestedBlog ? OK : NOT_FOUND
  };
}
